  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/98269269d196824e8756d0adf5ea8397.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/fa1f2e62b138b7e8d6a47e38d659d096.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Semi-Turn-Based, you need to develop a battle plan according to the battle environment and the characteristics of the enemy - targeting the enemy's weaknesses, assembling the right props and weapons for teammates; deploying teammates of various professions according to the progress of the battle, adjusting flexibly; Also, taking advantage of the terrain, such as heights and obstacles is a good idea. Try freeing your hands and fighting automatically if everything set done! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/7a212e62c3a1cf086c4b45fa8f2c6029.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/7a212e62c3a1cf086c4b45fa8f2c6029.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/dbf98af391fdc96540e0e79601f65150.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG with Tactical Semi-Turn-Based，character development, skill cultivation, equipment creation and so on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The teammate characters generated under the Roguelike, they all have randomly generated skills, attributes and talents; You need to choose the suitable cultivation route based on the available materials and the talents of the teammates; Choose the suitable partners to the team compilation, and set up a uniquely personalised battle squad to complete this Fated Journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/3a8c32fadcd68be8dbe721c3b059f6e5.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/3a8c32fadcd68be8dbe721c3b059f6e5.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/eed15fbf0bb7baa9086e800a302f5a94.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your team to explore and move freely in the world filled with puzzles and hidden objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all kinds of resources to build and upgrade your territory to expand and grow your team to meet all kinds of challenges! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/c1916a3551d22eb6dcf585bb1e34df52.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/c1916a3551d22eb6dcf585bb1e34df52.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/cf502f833f04e63259ad4afe5b1bb89f.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this continent, love and hate are intertwined between humans and elves, and there is an intricate connection... But with the resurrection of the Xenomorphs, which are extremely adaptable and reproducible and threaten both sides, humans and elves put aside their racial hatred for a while and face the challenge of survival together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/aa310d8eda366157085ca52afc06cfcd.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/aa310d8eda366157085ca52afc06cfcd.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/98269269d196824e8756d0adf5ea8397.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/fa1f2e62b138b7e8d6a47e38d659d096.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Semi-Turn-Based, you need to develop a battle plan according to the battle environment and the characteristics of the enemy - targeting the enemy's weaknesses, assembling the right props and weapons for teammates; deploying teammates of various professions according to the progress of the battle, adjusting flexibly; Also, taking advantage of the terrain, such as heights and obstacles is a good idea. Try freeing your hands and fighting automatically if everything set done! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/7a212e62c3a1cf086c4b45fa8f2c6029.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/7a212e62c3a1cf086c4b45fa8f2c6029.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/dbf98af391fdc96540e0e79601f65150.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG with Tactical Semi-Turn-Based，character development, skill cultivation, equipment creation and so on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The teammate characters generated under the Roguelike, they all have randomly generated skills, attributes and talents; You need to choose the suitable cultivation route based on the available materials and the talents of the teammates; Choose the suitable partners to the team compilation, and set up a uniquely personalised battle squad to complete this Fated Journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/3a8c32fadcd68be8dbe721c3b059f6e5.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/3a8c32fadcd68be8dbe721c3b059f6e5.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/eed15fbf0bb7baa9086e800a302f5a94.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your team to explore and move freely in the world filled with puzzles and hidden objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all kinds of resources to build and upgrade your territory to expand and grow your team to meet all kinds of challenges! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/c1916a3551d22eb6dcf585bb1e34df52.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/c1916a3551d22eb6dcf585bb1e34df52.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/cf502f833f04e63259ad4afe5b1bb89f.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this continent, love and hate are intertwined between humans and elves, and there is an intricate connection... But with the resurrection of the Xenomorphs, which are extremely adaptable and reproducible and threaten both sides, humans and elves put aside their racial hatred for a while and face the challenge of survival together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/aa310d8eda366157085ca52afc06cfcd.poster.avif?t=1748915352\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149850/extras/aa310d8eda366157085ca52afc06cfcd.webm?t=1748915352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
